<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ١٠٤ ... سُورَةُ الهُمَزَةِ ... آياتها ٩ ... مكية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَيْلٌ}</span> ... شَرٌّ، وَهَلَاكٌ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{هُمَزَةٍ}</span> ... مُغْتَابٍ لِلنَّاسِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لُّمَزَةٍ}</span> ... طَعَّانٍ فيِ النَّاسِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَعَدَّدَهُ}</span> ... أَحْصَاهُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَحْسَبُ}</span> ... يَظُنُّ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَخْلَدَهُ}</span> ... أَبْقَاهُ خَالِدًا فِي الدُّنْيَا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَلَّا}</span> ... لَيْسَ الأَمْرُ كَمَا يَظُنُّ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَيُنبَذَنَّ}</span> ... لَيُطْرَحَنَّ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْحُطَمَةِ}</span> ... النَّارِ الَّتِي تَهْشِمُ كُلَّ مَا يُلْقَى فِيهَا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَطَّلِعُ عَلَى الْأَفْئِدَةِ}</span> ... تَنْفُذُ لِشِدَّتِهَا مِنْ أَجْسَامِهِمْ إِلَى قُلُوبِهِمْ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُّؤْصَدَةٌ}</span> ... مُطْبَقَةٌ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فِي عَمَدٍ مُّمَدَّدَةٍ}</span> ... يُعَذَّبُونَ فِي أَعْمِدَةٍ طَوِيلَةٍ مِنَ النَّارِ، أَوْ أَنَّ أَبْوَابَهَا مُغْلَقَةٌ بِأَعْمِدَةٍ مُمَدَّدَةٍ؛ لِئَلَّا يَخْرُجُوا مِنْهَا.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>